item.description: Changelog # All notable changes to this project are documented in this page. The format is based on Keep a Changelog. 1.6.0-beta.2 - 2023-10-31 # Added # Small performance improve #641 Ability to prevent changing enablement of component #668 Changed # All logs passed to ErrorReport is now shown on the console log #643 Improved Behaviour with multi-material multi pass rendering #662 Previously, multi-material multi pass rendering are flattened. Since 1.
